"classified under ECCN ``5D002`` is not subject to the EAR when the "
"applicable conditions are met, and corresponding object code can also be "
"outside the EAR. Custom builds, hosted services, bundled distributions, and "
"downstream deployments should be evaluated as a whole by the exporting party."
