msgid ""
"Accelerator keys (also known as mnemonics) let users trigger a UI action "
"from the keyboard. They are marked in the string by a single punctuation "
"character, typically ``&`` (Qt, Windows), ``_`` (GTK), or ``~``. Literal "
"marker characters can usually be escaped by doubling them, and are ignored "
"by this check. Enable this check with the ``accelerator:`` flag to "
"explicitly choose the marker, for example ``accelerator:&``, "
"``accelerator:_``, or ``accelerator:~``."
